N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1273.10 - Use of fuel and lubricant facilities restricted

State Regulations

Unless otherwise provided in a lease or other agreement, all operators of aircraft who receive, and all persons who supply, aviation
fuel and lubricating oil at the air terminal, shall use only these aviation
fuel storage and delivery facilities designated by the airport operator for
such use. Notes
